quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Soab ning yɩ wagelle, Naam sẽn be a Soab nugẽ wã, Yẽnda yaa Tõod ne bũmbã fãa."
  67,2,"Sẽn naan-a kũum la vɩɩm, t'A na zarb yãmb n ges n bãng yãmb ned ning sẽn yɩɩd sõmblem ne tʋʋma."
  67,3,"Sẽn naan-a saas a yopoe n rog taaba, fo pa yãt Arrahmaan Naab naanegẽ wã yõs-taab ye, bɩ f yɩlem gesgo rẽ yĩnga fo nee võor bɩ?"
  67,4,"Rẽ poorẽ bɩ f yɩlem n ges yɩleng a yiibu, gesgã lebgdame n wa fo nengẽ t'a yaa koangd n yaa sũ-sãang soaba."
  67,5,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, Tõnd faasa Dũni saagã ne fɩtl-rãmbɑ, la Tõnd maan-a t'a yaa bõn-lobds Sʋɩtãambã yĩngã. Tõnd leb n segla bug-witg b yĩnga."
  67,6,"La be ne neb nins sẽn kɩfl-b ne b Soabã, Gεhanem naongo, la b lebeng zĩig me yi wẽnga."
  67,7,"B sã n lobg-b a pʋgẽ, b wʋmda a sẽn sesde t'a yaa sẽn kot wɑ rʋko."
  67,8,"A rat n na n pusgame sũ-puur keelem, wakat fãa b sã n lobg sull a pʋgẽ, a gũudbã yet-b lame:""bugsd pa wa yãmb nengẽ la?"""
  67,9,"Tɩ b yeele: ""n-yee! sɩd la hakɩɩka, bugsd waa tõnd nengẽ tɩ tõnd yagse la d yeele: Wẽnd pa sik ba fʋɩ, lɑ yãmb pa yɩ rẽndame tɩ y be meneng sẽn bedem pʋga""."
  67,10,"La b leb yeele: ""la tɩ tõnd sã n da yɩ n wʋmdame ma d ra tara yam, d kõon n zĩnd bug-witgã koɑmb pʋgẽ ye""."
  67,11,"Tɩ b sak n reeg b zunuubã b zugẽ; rẽnd bug-witmã kẽedb zĩig zãag yã!"
  67,12,"Ad neb nins sẽn yaeesd b Soabã ne A sẽn solgã fãa, bãmb-rãmb tara yaafg la keoor sẽn bεdme."
  67,13,"Y rat bɩ y solg y goamã, ma y vẽneg-a, ad Yẽ mii sẽn be sũyẽ pʋgẽ."
  67,14,"Rẽ yĩnga A pa mi A sẽn naane, tɩ Yẽ yaa minim zom Soaba n yaa a Tẽng-n-biiga."
  67,15,"Yẽ la Soab ning sẽn maan Tẽngã n kõ yãmb, tɩ yaa sẽn nome, bɩ y kẽn a weoon-vɩʋʋsẽ wã la y rɩ A rɩtlã, la lebengã zĩig yaa Yẽ nengẽ."
  67,16,"Rẽ yĩnga yãmb maana bas-m-yam ne Sẽn be-A saagẽ wã t'A kõ n bõrg yãmb ne Tẽngã, tɩ Tẽngã yaa sẽn dãmde?"
  67,17,"Bɩ yãmb maana bas-m-yam ne Sẽn be-A saagẽ wã t'A pɑ na n tʋms yãmb zug sob-fãeedga. Boto y na bãng Mam bugsgã sẽn ya-a soaba."
  67,18,"La sɩd-sɩda, neb nins sẽn reng bãmb taoorã yagsame, la Mam kisgrã yɩɩ wãn-wãna?."
  67,19,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb pa get liuuli wã bãmb zugẽ tɩ b yaa sẽn yεdgd b pɩgsã la b gõtẽ, bũmb pa gãt-b sã n pa Arrahmaan Naab ye; ad Yẽnda yaa Net ne bũmbã fãa gilli."
  67,20,"Bɩ yaa nin-bʋg n yaa yãmb fãagd n sõngd yãmba zẽng sẽn ka Arrahmaan Naaba? Kɩfr-dãmbã pa yɩ rallame tɩ b bee belg-m-meng pʋga."
  67,21,"Bɩ yaa ãnd n rɩlgd yãmb t'A sã n yõk A rɩtlã. Pa woto ye, b kell n raeega waoog-m-meng pʋgẽ la zoe n zãɑg pʋgẽ."
  67,22,"Rẽ yĩnga ned ning sẽn kẽnd-a t'a yaa sẽn suri, yẽ n yɩɩd sor bãngr bɩ yaa sẽn kẽnd-a tɩrg sorã zugu?"
  67,23,"Yeele: ""Yẽ la Soab ninga sẽn naan-a yãmba; A maana yãmb tɩ y tar tʋb la nin la sũyã; paood yãmb sẽn pʋʋsd barka""."
  67,24,"Yeele: ""Yẽ la Soab ning sẽn bõe yãmba, la b na n tigma yãmb A nengẽ""."
  67,25,"La b yetẽ: ""yaa rabʋr la pʋlen-kãngã, tɩ y sã n togsda sɩda"""
  67,26,"yeele: ""ad a bãngr bee Wẽnd nengẽ, la sã n ya ne maam, mam yaa bugsd n ya vẽnegd bala""."
  67,27,"Wakat ninga b sẽn wat n yã-a pẽem-pẽema, neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã nems sãamdame tɩ b yeel-ba: yãoã la bũmb ning yãmb sẽn da yɩ n yẽgemdẽ wã""."
  67,28,"Yeele: ""yãmb yãame, Wẽnd sã n kʋ maam la sẽn lagem-b maamã, ma A yols tõndo, rẽ fãɑ be A nungẽ, lɑ ãnd n na n fãag kɩfr-dãmb n yi naong sẽn zabde?"
  67,29,"Yeele: ""yaa Yẽ la Arrahmaan Naaba, tõnd kõo sɩd ne-A, Yẽ me la tõnd bobl d mens ne, la yãmb na bãng ned ning sẽn be meneng sẽn vẽneg pʋga""."
  67,30,"Yeele: ""yãmb yãame, yãmb koomã sã n vẽeg beoog t'a yaa sẽn fõoge, ãnd n na n wa ne ko-bundum yãmb nengẽ?"" ɑd kɑ be tɩ sã n pɑ Yẽ ye."
